= 2022


- Nov. 19, 2022, Invited talk in CSIAM Student Forum, [https://meeting.csiam.org.cn/\#/2022/ the 20th Annual Meeting of CSIAM]\n

- Sept. 20, 2022, /*\"Trust-region Subproblem Optimality Constraints for Under-determined Quadratic Model\"*/\n
(This is joint work with [http://lsec.cc.ac.cn/~yyx Prof. Ya-xiang Yuan], and presented in the group seminar @LSEC.)\n



